Package net.sourceforge.plantuml.sequencediagram

package net.sourceforge.plantuml.sequencediagram
Provides classes used to manage Sequence Diagram.

There are 2 architectures:

  1. net.sourceforge.plantuml.sequencediagram.puma (the current)
  2. net.sourceforge.plantuml.sequencediagram.teoz (the new)
    Can be activated using !pragma teoz true
